7. Service Blueprint

The service is delivered through the following interaction flow:

User
  ↓
Dashboard
  ↓
Matter Controller
  ↓
Border Router
  ↓
Gateway
  ↓
ESP32-C6 Sensor Nodes
Service Operation
Sensor nodes collect environmental data.
Data is transmitted to the Gateway.
The Border Router manages OpenThread connectivity.
Matter integrates devices and services.
The Dashboard presents information to users.
Users can send control commands.
Commands are delivered back to the actuator through the same infrastructure.
